 Amadeus Developers Portal (API signup & docs)

 https://developers.amadeus.com/

This is the main site where you register, create your app, and get your API key to start using Amadeus Flight APIs. You can also find full API documentation here. 


 What it does
Amadeus Flight APIs provide flight search, schedules, real-time pricing, availability, and booking used by apps like MakeMyTrip and Expedia (industry-standard GDS).

 How it works (flow)
User search → Flight Offers Search → price confirmation → Flight Create Order (booking) → booking management (PNR, cancel, view).

 Schedules & data
Supports future flight schedules and live availability in production; test environment provides cached/sample data for development.

 Free tier
Offers a free test environment and limited free monthly API calls; real-time booking beyond limits requires paid usage.
